{"tid":2339961,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"新公司名為X｜將旗下公司四合一？Tesla馬斯克：好主意！","createTime":"2020-12-25T05:32:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T04:37:30.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e335b6ab39f68022d6f108a0f30e669a759e444a","tid":2339961,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T05:32:10.000Z","msg":"Tesla行政總裁Elon Musk再有新想法！Elon Musk在一個Twitter回覆中透露將旗下四間公司合併的意向，並透過控股公司持有旗下四間旗艦公司，包括電動車公司Tesla、火箭公司SpaceX、腦神經科技公司Neuralink以及鑽探公司The Boring Company。YouTuber兼Tesla投資者Dave Lee更為公司「獻名」為X，Elon Musk在Twitter回覆：「好主意！」。<br />\n<br />\nDave Lee解釋，取名為X主要是因為Elon已經有域名<a href=\"http://x.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.com&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt7TKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=cd0ad3df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://x.com</a>，並認為這是一個「不錯的名字」。而新公司是一間「確保人類生存及進步」的公司。他又引述4至5年前已有報道指，Elon Musk對四間公司合併的意願，而新公司將可吸引更多具才華為工程師加入Musk企業團隊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://至於X.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%87%B3%E6%96%BCX.com&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt7TKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=5dbc8dca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">至於X.com</a>是Musk早在1999年注冊，當年他成立網上銀行，後來這間銀行與Confinity合併，從而成為PayPal，<a href=\"http://自此Musk擁有X.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%87%AA%E6%AD%A4Musk%E6%93%81%E6%9C%89X.com&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt7TKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=67f7a997\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">自此Musk擁有X.com</a>域名。<br />\n<br />\n有關消息傳出之後，有分析認為，Musk可以參考Google母企Alphabet的方案，2015年該公司進行重組，將所有與Google業務相關程度不大的公司或業務由Alphabet直接管理，成為Google的姊妹公司，這些公司包括人工智能公司Deep Mind、自動駕駛系統Waymo等，而Alphabet是各公司的集合體，最大資產仍是Google。不過有分於Alphabet，Musk旗下4間公司都是獨立實體，實際方案可能會有所不同。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201225/AX5LJ4EXNVA45FNBK54SE4KENA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201225%2FAX5LJ4EXNVA45FNBK54SE4KENA%2F&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt7TKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=156b668e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201225%2FAX5LJ4EXNVA45FNBK54SE4KENA%2F&h=78459fca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201225/AX5LJ4EXNVA45FNBK54SE4KENA/</a>"},{"pid":"db3515a87ca8fde296c9260fc2fd8a4f0649dd3d","tid":2339961,"uid":50660,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T05:34:23.000Z","msg":"如果X出現一定市值大過apple<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e720d143ccf616f5d5ed8bdf23c9a22e23cb48","tid":2339961,"uid":171668,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T05:39:30.000Z","msg":"美中不足美國鋼鐵用咗X"},{"pid":"dd869394fe04fad8ff8fd37d8b5eeba9dcbeea6d","tid":2339961,"uid":352873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T05:42:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cache.hkgolden.media/compress/http://i.imgur.com/FszPFOY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcache.hkgolden.media%2Fcompress%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FFszPFOY.gif&h=cef5560c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57992acde8fa484e985bd99a1f38295ec92797b7","tid":2339961,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46e720d143ccf616f5d5ed8bdf23c9a22e23cb48","tid":2339961,"uid":171668,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T05:39:30.000Z","msg":"美中不足美國鋼鐵用咗X"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T05:43:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n沒錯"},{"pid":"61b8a17de4eef49855883200c2056e5107ed8ab1","tid":2339961,"uid":9328,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T05:44:38.000Z","msg":"而新公司將可吸引更多具才<span class=\"red\">華為工程師</span>加入Musk企業團隊。"},{"pid":"f0d65332e7212ee6d87e8808246998f3a749c7fa","tid":2339961,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T05:47:49.000Z","msg":"mastrubation X!!!"},{"pid":"3d